I&#039;ve got two things to say:

As a big fan of RNS, their last rip was Fall Out
Boy, so why not closing my activity as a scener with the
same band? I had the fortune to get it as soon as now,
so...
I just want to dedicate this rip to my old friends, and
first of all to the old real LEGENDS of RNS. I will miss
you forever lads!
You gave me light to this world of sceners.

ASWELL, I want to dedicate this last rip to my other guys
who were with me thru all these past years!
THANKS A LOT, it was a pleasure to work with you!!!

I AM LEGEND.
FUCK THE HATERS!
